---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Model | èmote academy San Antonio" description="Discover our unique childcare model: a sanctuary with organic vegan meals, dynamic play, and low teacher-student ratios.">
	
	<section class="bg-amber-500 py-24 text-center px-6">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight mb-6">
				The Missing <span class="text-teal-900">Piece</span> of the Puzzle
			</h1>
			<p class="text-xl text-amber-50 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium">
				Welcome to a space where your child feels truly at ease—a second home designed with warmth, comfort, and care. 
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-20 px-6 bg-slate-50">
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20">
			
			<div class="space-y-12">
				<div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-teal-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-teal-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-teal-900 mb-4">Our Sanctuary</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						Our nurturing environment mirrors the love and security of home, easing the transition and alleviating the stress of separation. With attentive care and a focus on emotional well-being, we create the perfect foundation for learning, ensuring your child thrives academically and socially.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-green-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-teal-900 mb-4">Nourishing Inside Out</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						We take pride in offering freshly prepared meals that are vegan, vegetarian, allergen-free, and organic. Backed by our expertise in nutrition, we are dedicated to promoting kids' health through thoughtfully designed, balanced dishes that support growth and foster healthy eating habits.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="space-y-12">
				<div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-amber-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-teal-900 mb-4">Dynamic Play</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						Step into a vibrant space where every activity inspires joy. Outdoors, children engage in obstacle training, hopscotch, and sack races to build teamwork. Indoors, engaging puzzles and chess challenges sharpen critical thinking. Through dynamic play, we nurture competitive skills and emotional resilience.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-rose-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-rose-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-teal-900 mb-4">Teacher - Student Balance</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
						We prioritize a nurturing learning environment by maintaining optimal teacher-to-student ratios. Small group settings ensure personalized attention, while individual academic sessions are tailored to meet the unique needs and strengths of every child.
					</p>
					
					<div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100">
						<h3 class="font-bold text-teal-900 mb-2">The World in Our Words</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Discover the beauty of connection with our second language program. Through interactive songs and storytelling, children explore new languages while developing cultural awareness. We also partner with a specialized <strong>Speech Therapist</strong> to ensure confident communication.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>